Invocation Name: my practice
Developer Terms of Use
des: Practice Insights is a skill which helps dental practices and providers streamline day-to-day operations using Amazon Echo. Providers can ask Alexa about their next patient including arrival times, morning meeting report, production, collection, accounts receivables, scheduled patients, scheduled production, new patients and additional practice-related analytics powered by Sikka Software.
